Software requiremements
-----------------------
* Python 2.
* Epydoc just if document generation is needed.

Retrieve source code
--------------------
git clone https://github.com/skibyte/walldo.git

Building walldo
---------------
python2 setup.py build
This will create the files in the build directory.

Installing walldo
-----------------
python2 setup.py install
This will install walldo in the default path.

Installing walldo in a specific path
------------------------------------
python2 setup.py install --prefix=/usr
This will install walldo in usr directory.

Documentation generation
------------------------
epydoc --config=epydoc.conf
This will create a doc directory with the documentation in it.
